00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:29,812
<i>♪</i>

832
00:37:29,856 --> 00:37:32,772
- Oh, guess we're not gonna
see those dinosaurs.

833
00:37:34,339 --> 00:37:36,732
- Hey, gang. We need to
get the hell out of here.

