00:38:00,060 --> 00:38:02,236
You've potentially affected
thousands of lives.

848
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:05,283
- Yeah, and you just put
a huge target on our backs.

849
00:38:06,675 --> 00:38:09,678
<i>- We have another disturbance
